videos.description: Oregon State's Gligorije Rakocevic grabs the offensive rebound, then gets the putback layup to fall, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Oregon State's Gligorije Rakocevic gets the basket, plus the foul

videos.description: Arizona's Allonzo Trier drives to the basket and gets the layup, plus the foul.
videos.headline: Allonzo Trier drives and gets three the hard way

videos.description: Lauri Markkanen sinks a big 3-pointer, part of a 14-0 run for Arizona.
videos.headline: Lauri Markkanen spots up and nails the three

videos.description: Allonzo Trier blows by an Oregon State defender for the dunk.
videos.headline: Trier drives the baseline for the one-handed slam

videos.description: Corey Williams and Roxy Bernstein discuss Arizona's win over Oregon State with Wildcats guard Allonzo Trier
videos.headline: Corey Williams and Roxy Bernstein discuss Arizona's win over Oregon State with Wildcats guard Allonzo Trier

videos.description: Allonzo Trier scores 18 points off the bench and Arizona outscores Oregon State 44-25 in the second half en route to a 71-54 victory.
videos.headline: Arizona takes over in second half, routs Oregon State
